Package: gnome-shell-extension-language-border
Architecture: all
Depends: gnome-shell (>= 47), libglib2.0-bin, ${misc:Depends}
Description: GNOME Shell extension for window glow based on keyboard layout
 Adds a glow effect around windows that changes color depending on
 the current keyboard layout. Helps visually identify which language
 is active. Configurable colors, width and intensity for each layout.
 .
 Features:
  - Glow effect for active and passive windows
  - Per-language color customization (e.g., ru=green, us=red)
  - Settings panel via GNOME Extensions app
